article.linkText: Swain scores 37 to carry Yale past Columbia 83-72
article.story: NEW HAVEN, Conn. -- — Azar Swain scored a career-high 37 points with six 3-pointers as Yale topped Columbia 83-72 on Tuesday night. Jalen Gabbidon had 20 points for Yale (9-9, 3-1 Ivy League). Matt Knowling added eight rebounds. Ike Nweke had 21 points and nine rebounds for the Lions (4-13, 1-4). Geronimo Rubio De La Rosa added 16 points and Cameron Shockley-Okeke had 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
